# ─── API Keys & Secrets ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# NEVER commit your xAI API key!
# Supported locations (all gitignored):
#   - X_KEY (one-line file in project root, as documented)
#   - x_key.txt
#   - .env / .env.local (XAI_API_KEY=...)
X_KEY
x_key.txt
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
*.key
*.pem
secrets/

